  // Standard tabs
  section.section.section-lg.bg-white.text-center
    .shell
      h3 Standard tabs
      .range.range-50.range-md-center
        .cell-md-10.cell-lg-8
          #tabs-1.tabs-custom.tabs-horizontal.tabs-line
            // Nav tabs
            ul.nav.nav-tabs
              li.active: a(href='#tabs-1-1' data-toggle='tab') Overview
              li: a(href='#tabs-1-2' data-toggle='tab') Founder
              li: a(href='#tabs-1-3' data-toggle='tab') Mission

            // Tab panes
            .tab-content
              div#tabs-1-1.tab-pane.fade.in.active
                h5 Brave is an innovative web solution, which combines captivating design and flawless functionality in a multipurpose HTML template.
                p Made to be used by anyone who is looking for a stunning multifunctional website, this template is a universal solution, which can be used already after being installed. It differs from other similar projects in everything - be it the initial concept or the final look. Brave also can boast the set of powerful features that can be used by anyone without being afraid to overload their site.
                a.button.button-default-outline(href='#') learn more

              div#tabs-1-2.tab-pane.fade
                // Card info
                article.card-info
                  .card-info-aside
                    +jpg('roy-henry-150x150', 'card-info-image')
                  .card-info-main
                    h5.card-info-title Roy Henry
                    p.card-info-subtitle Founder
                    p Roy is the main person behind Brave. He is the multitalented manager and a former UX designer who is a true mine of creative ideas for everyone at our team.
                    a.button.button-default-outline(href='#') learn more

              div#tabs-1-3.tab-pane.fade
                .box-width-2
                  p In the digital age, we are marketing ourselves on the web.  That is why we aim to make it as easy and affordable for everyone to take charge of their web presence.  Words like tweet and yelp should be part of your marketing campaign, and not part of your stress.
                  // Quote minimal
                  article.quote-minimal
                    p.quote-minimal-text We strive to create a memorable web image for everyone.
                  p We establish a relationship with all of our clients, and we feel it is our responsibility to help them grow and harness the opportunity of their presence on the Internet.
                  a.button.button-default-outline(href='#') learn more
  ="\n"

